647
00:39:53,925 --> 00:39:55,686
Io no, ma Rosa sicuro fa piacere.

648
00:39:59,487 --> 00:40:00,489
Dai, su, fammi vedere.

649
00:40:02,309 --> 00:40:02,570
Cosa?

650
00:40:03,471 --> 00:40:03,831
Adesso?

651
